#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>ldap</acronym> is the lightweight directory access protocol. It "
"provides access to an X.500 directory, or to a stand-alone <acronym>LDAP</"
"acronym> server."
msgstr ""
"<acronym>LDAP</acronym> 是 lightweight directory access protocol (轻量目录访"
"问协议) 的缩写。它提供对 X.500 目录或者 <acronym>LDAP</acronym> 独立服务器的"
"访问支持。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can use the ldap KIO worker as follows:"
msgstr "您可以通过以下方式使用 LDAP KIO 工作程序："

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>ldap://host:port/ou=People,o=where,c=de??sub</userinput> for a "
"subtree-query"
msgstr ""
"输入 <userinput>ldap://host:port/ou=People,o=where,c=de??sub</userinput> 以进"
"行子树查询"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"or <userinput>ldap://host:port/cn=MM,ou=People,o=where,c=de??base</"
"userinput> for a complete branch."
msgstr ""
"或者输入 <userinput>ldap://host:port/cn=MM,ou=People,o=where,c=de??base</"
"userinput> 进行完整分支查询。"
